snippet.title: Maid Of Sker Gameplay - Developer Presentation - Future Games Show
snippet.description: Maid Of Sker is a first person horror game where even your breathing can get you killed. Maid of Sker launches on PS4, Xbox, Switch and Windows in June 2020
